title: Rand Paul Wins New Hampshire Straw Poll
text: Republican presidential candidate Rand Paul has scored another victory in his campaign for the presidency. Yesterday, Senator Paul won the straw poll at the Republican Liberty Caucus National Convention in New Hampshire. As the Hill reported, the poll had around 800 participants.
